    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "lbl_default",
      "x": 100, "y": 200,
      "width": 1200, "height": 60,
      "text": "Default lifecycle is [\"pending\", \"done\"] — old sweeps work unchanged.\nThe DAG below is what the retro skill would configure for finding-tracking.",
